    "body": "Fix https://github.com/KMiri-rs/KMiri/issues/51\r\n\r\n`Cell::default` and `Cell::new(\"\")` now differs since https://github.com/ratatui/ratatui/pull/2150:\r\n* `default` has zero column_span, which doesn't render the cell at all\r\n* `new` has one column_span, which renders the cell as a column like before\r\n\r\nThe table looks good by replacing the Cell constructor\r\n<img width=\"3326\" height=\"1031\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/acd41538-1baf-482b-9e11-2e4278f6cae4\" />\r\n",
