        },
        "message": "debugger(stacked_borrows): fix empty_cell due to newly added column_span\n\nThe default function of Cell has zero column_span, causing the cell not\nrendered.\n\nAllocId   BasePaddr      Kind      Names     Bytes     Align PosStart    PosEnd   BorTagID  StackIdx      Permission Protected   Exposed PrevTagID  RetagInfo\n173        0xfffff8     Stack                  8 B       8 B        0         8         17         0  SharedReadOnly                            11 [f] Normal\n       10         1    Unique\n174        0xfffff0     Stack                  8 B       8 B        0         8         18         0  SharedReadOnly                            13 [f] Normal\n       12         1    Unique\n175        0xffffe0     Stack                 16 B       8 B        0        16         19         0  SharedReadOnly                            15 [f] Normal\n       14         1    Unique\n10406      0xfa3b28     Stack   iter,_31      16 B       8 B        0         8      29835         0          Unique        ✅               29834    FnEntry\n    29834         1 ReadWrite                          29833 TwoPhase\n    29833         2    Unique         ✅               29832  FnEntry\n    29832         3 ReadWrite                          29831 TwoPhase\n    29831         4    Unique                          29794   Normal\n    29794         5    Unique\n        8        16     29839          0 dReadOnly        ✅              29837    FnEntry\n    29837         1 dReadOnly                          29835   Normal\n    29835         2    Unique         ✅               29834  FnEntry\n    29834         3 ReadWrite                          29833 TwoPhase\n    29833         4    Unique         ✅               29832  FnEntry\n    29832         5 ReadWrite                          29831 TwoPhase\n    29831         6    Unique                          29794   Normal\n    29794         7    Unique\n\nThe fix is using the new function which has one column_span.\n\nAllocId   BasePaddr      Kind      Names     Bytes     Align PosStart    PosEnd   BorTagID  StackIdx      Permission Protected   Exposed PrevTagID  RetagInfo\n173        0xfffff8     Stack                  8 B       8 B        0         8         17         0  SharedReadOnly                            11 [f] Normal\n                                                                                        10         1          Unique\n174        0xfffff0     Stack                  8 B       8 B        0         8         18         0  SharedReadOnly                            13 [f] Normal\n                                                                                        12         1          Unique\n175        0xffffe0     Stack                 16 B       8 B        0        16         19         0  SharedReadOnly                            15 [f] Normal\n                                                                                        14         1          Unique\n10406      0xfa3b28     Stack er,_30,_31      16 B       8 B        0        16      29832         0 SharedReadWrite                         29831   TwoPhase\n                                                                                     29831         1          Unique                         29794     Normal\n                                                                                     29794         2          Unique\n\nThis change was introduced since\nhttps://github.com/ratatui/ratatui/commit/f9d066f4d74684bb13fbbac6c02fb1178d9c0b15#diff-f0b771568df73b874b80efa84af23a8f1e31a4b0e98bdd41c4205cad5a093986",
